# [Aa]ssets/[Aa]ddressable[Aa]ssets[Dd]ata/*/AddressablesBuildTEP.json
# [Aa]ssets/[Aa]ddressable[Aa]ssets[Dd]ata/*/catalog*.json
# [Aa]ssets/[Aa]ddressable[Aa]ssets[Dd]ata/*/catalog*.hash

